NAME
    mnimograph.pl

AUTHOR
    Dimitrios - Georgios Kontopoulos

DESCRIPTION
    mnimograph.pl is a tool for memory usage graphing.

    It will collect memory usage values every 5 seconds until being stopped
    by typing 'Q' and pressing <Enter>.

    Its output is a graph of the values in .eps format.

DEPENDENCIES
    -Gnuplot ( >= 4.4 )

    -Perl ( >= 5.14.2 )

    -Chart::Gnuplot ( >= 0.17 )

    -Term::ReadKey ( >= 2.30 )

USAGE
    mnimograph.pl output_filename

